{"tid":85131,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我是一個弧兒","createTime":"2017-01-18T05:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T15:32:20.000Z","uid":6230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee23a65856fff8d2eaf2d4c3efa39e2d1a7e704","tid":85131,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:53:29.000Z","msg":"鈴&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n這是2007學期最後一個鐘聲。<br />\n後邊傳來一把聲音「阿維，放學去邊呀？去唔去Neway唱K？」<br />\n答「唔喇，應承左阿媽番去食飯。」<br />\n我叫阿維，１８歲，讀完中三。<br />\n我的同學年紀都比我小兩年，原因不是我成績差而留級。<br />\n而是我是一個弧兒，遲了兩年才入學。<br />\n對！那個「阿媽」是我養母。"},{"pid":"f7bce3bb37619fd2c01f4172a62f8967f9f268b4","tid":85131,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:53:57.000Z","msg":"So?"},{"pid":"7ad06afdd412c483033161d5ccb68f59d2cd1070","tid":85131,"uid":65932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:35:02.000Z","msg":"咩係弧兒？"},{"pid":"08d211be7e2fb6796da35e7af614e56c96649f1e","tid":85131,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:39:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩係弧兒？</blockquote><br />\n打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c858009c8fb7500e8ce2cd7999ffc1292ea156cc","tid":85131,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f7dff5a4e77f4acd6c691c8b3cf913f10d1505","tid":85131,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T18:38:05.000Z","msg":"「媽咪，返黎喇。」<br />\n媽：「daddy今晚唔洗ot，我地等埋佢先食飯啦。」<br />\n「知道。」<br />\n不知不覺已經習慣了她就是我媽媽，十年前就是她帶我回來。<br />\n<br />\n沙⋯（浴室水聲）<br />\n<br />\n涼已沖，水已乾。<br />\n爸爸回來了，他是個大忙人，很難得可以同枱食飯，他在一家中小企任職經理，可以話係第二把膠椅。<br />\n<br />\n爸問：「阿維，放暑假喇喎，有冇咩計劃？」<br />\n「游水打波去街打機，都係咁啦。」<br />\n爸：「咁樣樣，不如我地去個旅行，去沖繩玩啦，好冇呀老婆？」<br />\n媽答：「唉，你半年前夠話去北海道過聖誕啦，最後咪比你老闆扣留住⋯」<br />\n爸回應：「放心，今次一定得！阿維食完飯幫我睇機票。」<br />\n「好，冇問題。」<br />\n<br />\n飯後我就開著電腦，做下資料搜集，很快就找了幾間做比較，心想先儲存下來明天才給爸爸看，任務完成，之後當然打機啦，當時只喜歡一隻online game&mdash;龍族，<br />\n雖然只是私服，但已足夠了。<br />\n<br />\n玩了不知多少個小時，我睡著了⋯"},{"pid":"b0d3b212f0a49ff5cf13caadc043fc7da74af59e","tid":85131,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T19:13:48.000Z","msg":"因為尿急，醒了。<br />\n剛睡醒，人不是太清醒，隱隱約約聽到有把女人呼叫聲。<br />\n不，是呼吸聲。<br />\n基於好奇，我想搵出聲音來源，另一方面又害怕，怕不知是人或是鬼。<br />\n下一秒鐘，聲音愈來愈大，我發現好明顯是爸媽房間傳出來。<br />\n一步一步逼近房門，呼吸聲愈趨清楚，雖然我是一個青頭仔，但性教育課我也有上，成績都不錯！我李爾維大膽講句佢地正在做愛做的事！<br />\n突然，呼吸聲無了，剩下空氣流動與我的心跳聲，卜卜⋯卜卜⋯卜卜⋯<br />\n<br />\n「鴉！」一聲後呼吸聲回來了。<br />\n呼氣更頻密，開始有點上氣唔接下氣。<br />\n<br />\n因為剛才小解還未完成，同時小弟弟開始漲大了，變了大弟弟，我知道現在一定不可以順暢地去小解，所以我選擇了繼續企，人生有時候乜都唔做就是最好的解決方法。<br />\n<br />\n兩分鐘後，這個樂團多了兩件敲擊樂，<br />\n一床架的搖晃聲，二身體的碰撞聲。"},{"pid":"140efc3815f928be8b7e31a091a4758ac4e41685","tid":85131,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9df554f0210bfd5037d2f77a0a72d6cfe971a0","tid":85131,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T02:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0939a98185228daafff9d28cb8c8c2a5700bdbc4","tid":85131,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"屌，冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660a6987255bb85f343a4e27d5e984a031b059aa","tid":85131,"uid":4158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97433db1a8ea0da293aef20acdb32230bfbceebb","tid":85131,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T12:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6144e110a47831cffb31b504171dcc69e9beed4","tid":85131,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601af0cda11c94f8d1b415bb957b750844a3133a","tid":85131,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d251f0269bb8cfc45b4c5e6b072856a066df44d4","tid":85131,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeeb208154da624f1adf0d1f9bc3dfc00c580aa1","tid":85131,"uid":6230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T15:29:32.000Z","msg":"第一次寫，比d意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d17b1c48a903ccd0ce71cfabf7b1c4896e4ccb","tid":85131,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"得咁短&hellip;不過支持"}]}